#: upstream/_posts/2020-05-05-introducing-command-mode.adoc:75
#, fuzzy
msgid "``` quarkus.log.level=SEVERE quarkus.hibernate-orm.log.sql=false quarkus.banner.enabled=false ```"
msgstr "<pre class=\"highlight\"> ``</pre>"

